"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/1077611","Department for International Trade","false","2019-03-06","<p>UKEF’s mission is to ensure no viable UK export fails for lack of finance or insurance from the private sector. Its support is available for UK exports from all sectors.</p><p> </p><p>We have no plans to review UKEF’s remit to support UK exports.</p>","Beverley and Holderness","Graham Stuart","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/1077611/answer",,,,,,"2019-03-06T16:57:40.507Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/1077611/answer","Biography information for Graham Stuart","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/1077611/answer",,,,,,,,"202","International Trade","International Trade","2019-02-26","Oil and Natural Gas: Export Credit Guarantees","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for International Trade, whether he plans to review UK Export Finance policy on awarding funds to support businesses involved in oil and gas schemes globally.","false","Biography information for Catherine West","Hornsey and Wood Green","Catherine West","226187"
"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/1077612","Ministry of Housing, Communities and Local Government","false","2019-03-06","<p>The final report of the review, chaired by the member for West Dorset, was published alongside the Budget in October. The Government will respond to the review shortly.</p>","Old Bexley and Sidcup","James Brokenshire","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/1077612/answer",,,,,,"2019-03-06T11:53:28.11Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/1077612/answer","Biography information for James Brokenshire","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/1077612/answer",,,,,,,,"7","Housing, Communities and Local Government","Housing, Communities and Local Government","2019-02-26","Build Out Rates Independent Review","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Housing, Communities and Local Government, when the Government plans to respond to the Independent Review of Build Out.","false","Biography information for John Healey","Wentworth and Dearne","John Healey","226043"
